		<h3> </h3>     
		<h1>Obama's Speech at Woodrow Wilson Center</h1>
                          		<p class="pub-info">
            		    Speaker: Barack Obama<br />                            

            			Published August 1, 2007<br />
			            
		</p>		
 <!--googleon: snippet--> 
    <article>

<div id="intro-pullout" class="no-bottom-padding">
                <h4>Share</h4>
        <div class="share-wrapper--vertical-share-widget">
